Namespace: {{ .Namespace }}

**Prerequisites:** This component requires an OLM operator to be pre-installed in the cluster.

## Deploy

```bash
# Create namespace
kubectl create namespace {{ .Namespace }} --dry-run=client -o yaml | kubectl apply -f -

# Apply custom resources
kubectl apply -f resources.yaml -n {{ .Namespace }}
```

## Verify

```bash
# Check custom resources
kubectl get -f resources.yaml -n {{ .Namespace }}
```

## Undeploy

```bash
# Delete custom resources
kubectl delete -f resources.yaml -n {{ .Namespace }} --ignore-not-found
```
